  "merger_description": "Coles Group Limited (**Coles**) is an Australian public company (ASX: COL) that primarily operates:\n\n* supermarkets nationwide through its subsidiary, Coles Supermarkets Australia Pty Ltd; and\n* retail liquor stores nationwide, trading under the Liquorland, Liquorland Warehouse and Liquorland Cellars brands.\n\nH.A. Bachrach (Nom) Pty Ltd (the\u00a0**Lessor**) is a part of an Australian private property development company, the Bachrach Naumburger Group, which manages a portfolio of commercial office and retail properties in Queensland.\n\nColes has signed a letter of offer in respect of a proposed lease for the development of a Coles supermarket within an existing shopping centre known as Park Beach Plaza, located at 253 Pacific Highway, Coffs Harbour, NSW 2450 (the **Acquisition**). The site was previously occupied by a Ritchies IGA Supermarket which closed at the end of April 2026.\n\nThe proposed Coles supermarket is anticipated to open in September 2027.",
